OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775675472
OL,3,CWhat can Starmer achieve in the Gulf?
OL,5,FHours after US President Donald Trump
OL,6,Fannounced a two-week cessation of
OL,7,Fhostilities against Iran, I travelled
OL,8,Fto the Gulf with the prime minister
OL,9,Fand his team on board the official
OL,10,Fgovernment plane. We have just landed
OL,11,Fin Saudi Arabia.
OL,13,FFor diplomatic and security reasons, I
OL,14,Fhave been asked not to disclose our
OL,15,Fitinerary or Prime Minister Keir
OL,16,FStarmer's schedule of meetings with
OL,17,Fgovernment heads.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
