CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775675472
OL,3,CWhat can Starmer achieve in the Gulf?
OL,5,FHowever, I don't have a clue how their
OL,6,Frespective positions on Iran's nuclear
OL,7,Fambitions or Iran's determination to
OL,8,Fbe turnpike keeper of the Hormuz
OL,9,FStrait can be bridged.
OL,11,FBecause the Hormuz Strait is the
OL,12,Fsupply route for a fifth of the
OL,13,Fworld's carbon energy, and therefore a
OL,14,Fkind of oesophagus for the global
OL,15,Feconomy, much of Starmer's focus in
OL,16,Ftalks with Gulf leaders will be a
OL,17,Fcontinuation of British diplomatic
OL,18,Factivity with 40-odd other nations in
OL,19,Frecent days, namely whether there is
OL,20,Fany practical way to make the Strait
OL,21,Fsafe for commercial traffic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
