PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775675472
OL,3,CWhat can Starmer achieve in the Gulf?
OL,5,FBut his other message is bound to be
OL,6,Falong the lines of "when this chaos is
OL,7,Ffinally over, don't forget who your
OL,8,Ftrue allies and friends are."
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThe point is that - like Starmer -
OL,16,Fnone of the Gulf states wanted Trump
OL,17,Fto attack Iran when he did.
OL,26,@nD@TOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
