OL,3,CWhat can Starmer achieve in the Gulf?
OL,5,FAnd although the UK's military has
OL,6,Fbeen exposed by both the Ukraine and
OL,7,FIran conflicts as depleted and
OL,8,Funequipped for this era of drone wars,
OL,9,Fthe UK has been deploying planes and
OL,10,Fweapons to protect the region from
OL,11,FIran's assorted uncrewed aerial
OL,12,Fthreats.
OL,14,FIn the eyes of Gulf leaders, the UK -
OL,15,Fand Europe more widely, including
OL,16,FUkraine with its formidable drone
OL,17,Fcapabilities - presumably looks a less
OL,18,Fintimidating friend than either
OL,19,FAmerica or China. They have a material
OL,20,Finterest in strengthening ties with
OL,21,FBritain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775675472
OL,3,CWhat can Starmer achieve in the Gulf?
OL,5,FThis is important because Trump's Iran
OL,6,Fwar is reconfiguring the global
OL,7,Fbalance of power in a fundamental way.
OL,9,FFor Starmer and the UK there are
OL,10,Frisks, especially if the US were to
OL,11,Fprecipitously withdraw its military
OL,12,Fumbrella from our continent. And to be
OL,13,Fclear, there is no sign of Starmer
OL,14,Funilaterally abandoning the UK's
OL,15,Fhistoric entente with America, even if
OL,16,FTrump is an unreliable and sometimes
OL,17,Fabusive friend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775675472
OL,3,CWhat can Starmer achieve in the Gulf?
OL,5,FBut in this dangerous world, a medium-
OL,6,Fsized nation like the UK needs as much
OL,7,Fgoodwill as it can muster in the
OL,8,Finternational community.
OL,10,FIn the coming days I will try to gauge
OL,11,Fwhether the leaders in this region are
OL,12,Fsimply going through the motions in
OL,13,Fseeing Starmer or whether he can
OL,14,Frecreate some of the warmth - and
OL,15,Fsignificant commercial advantage -
OL,16,Fthat was generated and enjoyed by
OL,17,FThatcher.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
